Don't know if it is due to the same reason, but I am also seeing some regressions in the 1.4 - 1.5 and 1.5 - 1.6 updates, as reported in #19027 (with reproducible snippet).
In my example, the slowdown happens in CPU computations, and the code becomes 100x slower. Not sure where it is due to tensorflow, to keras, or to anaconda compilation flags.
